"index_reference": "5031: knowledge, of sin",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Originating with the fall, it is revealed by conscience, the law and the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<h2>Knowledge of sin as a result of the fall</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:13\">GEN 3:1–3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22\">GEN 3:22</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of sin through conscience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:14-Rom2:15\">ROM 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:5-1Sam24:6\">1SA 24:5–24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:10\">2SA 24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of sin through the law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20\">ROM 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:13\">ROM 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:7\">ROM 7:7</a></p>\n<h3>The law was taught to all in Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:11\">LEV 10:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:1\">DEU 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:31\">DEU 5:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:9\">DEU 6:6–6:9</a></p>\n<h2>Knowledge of sin through the convicting power of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7-John16:11\">JHN 16:7–16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a></p>",
